      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SATONO INVADER (1) made it four top-two finishes from four career runs when she drove hard late to just arrive in time over this distance at Taree last time out. Meets a deeper field here but she is full of promise and keeps raising the bar. GAMING (6) raced four-wide but wouldn't lie down last start and was only two lengths off the winner over today's journey at Grafton. Up in class but drops 4.5kgs. Draws a better gate so expect him to be in the finish. TALANA (3) put the writing on the wall at his latest run when beaten under a length by SATONO INVADER. Gets a 1.5 kg weight swing so has to be considered. THEDAYTHEMUSICDIED (5) tackles a better race today but she is flying and enjoys racing at Coffs.",
